==生平==
福格尔是英国女演员[[朱莉娅·福斯特|朱莉娅·福斯特]]和[[加拿大|加拿大]]外籍兽医[[布鲁斯·福格尔|布鲁斯·福格尔]]的儿子。他曾就读于两所独立的学校：位于[[伦敦|伦敦]][[汉普斯特得|汉普斯特得]]的霍尔学校和[[多塞特郡|多塞特郡]]布兰福德社区的[[布莱恩斯滕|布莱恩斯滕]]学校，之后又就读[[朴茨茅斯大学|朴茨茅斯大学]]和[[哥斯达黎加大学|哥斯达黎加大学]]。<ref>Appleyard, Diana (24 July 2009). [http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-1201899/Me-school-photo-Ben-Fogle-remembers-homesick-boarding-school-days-struggled-dyslexia.html "Me and My School Photo: Ben Fogle Remembers His Homesick Boarding School Days and How He Struggled with Dyslexia"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-1201899/Me-school-photo-Ben-Fogle-remembers-homesick-boarding-school-days-struggled-dyslexia.html |date=20150707213546 }}. ''[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]''.  Retrieved 9 July 2012.</ref>褔格尔成为皇家海军预备役的学生，在HMS Blazer号巡逻艇上担任{{Link-en|大學皇家海軍訓練隊|University Royal Naval Unit|大學儲備军官}}。<ref>{{cite web|title=Chat with Ben Fogle! {{!}} Mayhem! Magazine|url=http://www.mayhemmagazine.co.uk/blog/2011/12/catch-up-with-ben-fogle/|accessdate=10 August 2013|archive-date=2013-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130909073810/http://www.mayhemmagazine.co.uk/blog/2011/12/catch-up-with-ben-fogle/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

